t=0
draw=_=>{t||createCanvas(W=720,W)
t+=.005
colorMode(HSB)
B=blendMode
B(BLEND)
background(0,.1)
B(ADD)
noFill()
for(y=0;y<W;y+=17)for(x=-y/17%2*17;x<W;x+=34)stroke((N=noise(x/200,y/200,t)*6+t)*W%360,90,W,(T=tan(N)**8))+square(x-(S=min(13,W/T)),y-S,S*2)}
